BEGIN
SELECT * FROM [EMPLOYEE] WHERE
[Ssn] like @Search or Fname like @Search or Minit like @Search or Lname like @Search or Bdate like @Search or Address like @Search or Sex like @Search or Salary like @Search or Super_ssn like @Search or Dno like @Search
END

Property.Value:
BEGIN
UPDATE[EMPLOYEE] set
Fname = @Fname, Minit = @Minit, Lname = @Lname, Bdate = @Bdate, Address = @Address, Sex = @Sex, Salary = @Salary, Super_ssn = @Super_ssn, Dno = @Dno
WHERE Ssn = @Ssn
END
